name: Pro Size Zebra Makeup Brush Roll
description:
Hello and thank you for checking out my item! This is a handmade one of a kind Pro Size Zebra Brush roll where you can use to store your makeup brushes whether you are a professional makeup artist or just a makeup lover! This brush roll is handmade by me and use cotton fabric on the outside and a faux leather interior for easy cleaning. Just wipe away with a damp towel or very simply just hand wash it and hang to air dry. This measures approximately 20 inches long and 12 inches high. the slots are about 2 inches wide and you can fit from 3 big powder brushes or 6 thin brushes on each slot approximately 10 slots on the roll. please allow 2-3 days for fabrication and to ship them. I ship from los angeles california and standard shipping is what i use unless otherwise stated. Comes from a smoke and pet free home!
Have any questions? email me at makeupartist_liz@yahoo.com ( i can also send you more pictures of the inside of the roll to your email if you would like.
Thank you for looking!!!
